# Triftly sheet & trips UI patterns

Do not regress these patterns when editing Trips or Tools.

## Opening any bottom sheet

Use `TriftlyBottomSheet.show(context, child: …)` — **not** raw `showModalBottomSheet`.

**Exception:** `TripDatePickerSheet.show` and `TripTimePickerSheet.show` are the public API for pickers — they wrap `showModalBottomSheet` internally with the correct flags. Callers must use `.show`, never `showDatePicker` / `showTimePicker` / a raw modal.

Required modal flags (handled by helper):
- `showDragHandle: false`
- `useRootNavigator: true`
- `backgroundColor: Colors.transparent`
- `isScrollControlled: true`

Dismiss via **swipe down** unless the sheet has its own confirm action.

## Confirmations (`confirm_bottom_sheet.dart`)

Use **`ConfirmBottomSheet.show`** — **not** centered `AlertDialog` or `showDialog` for destructive / yes-no flows.

```dart
final ok = await ConfirmBottomSheet.show(
  context,
  title: 'Delete trip?',
  message: '“${trip.name}” will be removed from your list.',
  confirmLabel: 'Delete',
  destructive: true,
);
if (ok && context.mounted) { /* act */ }
```

- Launched via `TriftlyBottomSheet.show` (same flags as other sheets).
- **Liquid glass** floating card: `GlassSurface` + `SpendGlassShell.tint`, frosted icon well.
- **Single action:** `SwipeToConfirm` (same as sign-out in `user_detail_bottom_sheet.dart`) — swipe right to confirm; dismiss by swiping the sheet down.
- `destructive: true` → `SwipeToConfirmStyle.destructive` — track fills **full red** at 100% swipe (sign-out pattern).
- Optional `swipeLabel` (default: `Slide to {confirmLabel}`).

## Sheet scaffold (`sheet_scaffold.dart`)

Two sheet types share the same chrome:

### A. Form sheets (create trip, add spot)
- `SheetScaffold(showCloseButton: false)` — **no** scaffold `title` / `subtitle`
- Drag handle **inside** `SheetScaffold` (default)
- Hero field at top (`SheetHeroField`)
- Sections: `SheetSectionHeader` + `SheetSoftCard`
- Fields: borderless (`SheetInlineField`, `SheetIconFieldRow`) — **no** `OutlineInputBorder`
- Submit: `SheetScaffold.swipeForm` (pins `SwipeToConfirm` in footer) — **not** inline in scroll body
- Short forms (sign-in): `SheetScaffold.swipeForm(compact: true)` — sheet hugs content, swipe footer pinned
- Submit control: `SwipeToConfirm` — **not** `FilledButton` / `SheetPrimaryButton`
- Trip sheets outside page `BlocProvider`: wrap with `BlocProvider.value`

### B. Utility sheets (tools, settlement, pickers)
- `SheetScaffold(showCloseButton: false)` — **no** scaffold `title` / `subtitle`
- Tool name via `SheetSectionHeader(title:, caption:)` as **first child** in body
- Content in `SheetSoftCard`
- Actions: `SheetPrimaryButton` for lookup/apply (not Material `FilledButton`)
- Results: `SheetResultBanner`
- Mode toggles: `SheetChoiceChipRow` (not `SegmentedButton` / dropdowns)

## Shared primitives (`sheet_form_primitives.dart`)

| Widget | Use |
|--------|-----|
| `SheetSectionHeader` | In-body title + optional caption (caption stacks below title) |
| `SheetSoftCard` | Grouped form / tool content |
| `SheetHeroField` | Primary named input (forms) |
| `SheetInlineField` | Borderless text/number input |
| `SheetIconFieldRow` | Icon tile + inline field |
| `SheetCurrencyChipPicker` | Flag + symbol chips only |
| `SheetChoiceChipRow` | 2–3 mode segments |
| `SheetNumericHeroField` | Large amount / result with symbol affix |
| `SheetPrimaryButton` | Utility sheet CTA (gradient; tools, share, pickers) |
| `SheetCardActionRow` | In-card footer row with chevron (sign-in Continue) |
| `SheetOptionRow` | Selectable list rows (appearance, currency, menus) |
| `SheetSoftListDivider` | Indented divider inside zero-padding `SheetSoftCard` |
| `SheetCompactAction` | Small in-row action chip (Paid, Everyone) |
| `SheetResultBanner` | Converted / lookup result |

## Segment control (`trip_phase_segment.dart`)

See **`filter-tabs-ui.mdc`** for the full filter-tab pattern (liquid glass + icons).

- **Active** tab only: live ripple rings + pulsing dot when selected.
- Phase colors: Active = orange, Upcoming = light blue, Done = grey.

## New Trip sheet (`create_trip_bottom_sheet.dart`)
- App bar **+** opens sheet. `SwipeToConfirm` label **"Slide to create trip"**.
- `BlocProvider.value(value: tripListBloc)` required.
- Uses shared primitives: `SheetHeroField`, `SheetSectionHeader`, `SheetSoftCard`, `SheetIconFieldRow`, `SheetCurrencyChipPicker`.

## Add Spot sheet (`add_spot_bottom_sheet.dart`)
- Same chrome as create trip. `SwipeToConfirm` **"Slide to add spot"**.
- `BlocProvider.value(value: tripDetailBloc)` required.

## Inline action menus (plan spot, trip card, buddies)
- Use **`GlassContextMenu.show`** — **not** `PopupMenuButton`.
- See **`liquid-glass-ui.mdc`** → Context menus for trigger, entries, width, and destructive styling.
- **Plan spot row** (`plan_tab.dart` `_SpotActionsMenu`): maps, visited toggle, expense, edit, delete — delete is `destructive: true`.
- **Trip card** (`trip_card.dart` `_TripMenu`): edit / delete or leave.
- **Trip detail app bar ⋮** → `TripDetailMenuSheet` (bottom sheet with `SheetOptionRow`) — not `GlassContextMenu`.

## Currency (`currency_options.dart`)
- Chips: **flag + symbol** only (e.g. 🇯🇵 ¥). No country name on chips.

## Date / time pickers
- `TripDatePickerSheet.show` — not `showDatePicker` (picker sheet owns the modal launcher)
- `TripTimePickerSheet.show` for spot / flight times (same exception as date picker)
- Picker UI is travel-themed custom chrome — not Material `showDatePicker`

